For an adopter's tool using wtp in headless mode, certain loaded emf resources sometimes get unloaded prematurely by ResourceSetWorkbenchEditSynchronizer.  This causes the loaded EMF objects from those resources to go proxy and various failures then occur.  This is a pretty serious problem that seems to be specific to headless eclipse mode only.

